	title = {The Cyber Range: A Guide},
	abstract = {Cybersecurity is a twenty first century challenge requiring a twenty first century workforce. The current cybersecurity workforce lacks sufficient professionals with the skills, training, and credentials to meet this cutting edge challenge. Market studies predict that this talent and skills gap will continue to widen among current and prospective cyber professionals over the coming years, creating a tremendous risk to business, government, and society.},
